     "prose": {
      "en": "This section provides guidance on securing aspects of the local users and groups.\n\n**Note:** The recommendations in this section check local users and groups. Any users or groups from other sources such as LDAP will not be audited. In a domain environment similar checks should be performed against domain users and groups."
